description: What's it going to be then, eh? A bit of the old in/out it seems for young Cody Cummings. He's found himself a pretty little lass that is very much to his liking. Heather Vahn should learn to keep her windows shut, what with all these lurking roust-abouts hanging around at night. One can never be too careful, less they should find themselves face to face with one of the more sordid of these hooligans, and subjected to his lurid juvenile fantasies of sexual and moral degradation. Probably gonna have to deep throat him as well. Enjoy!
title: Cockwork Cody
